        <Param val="instruction_text = &quot;You have completed the practice trials. During the experimental trials, you will not receive feedback, but it is very important that you respond as quickly and accurately as possible.\nBefore you begin, please ensure that you are in a comfortable and quiet location and will not be disturbed for about 10 minutes, as the experiment cannot be paused and we cannot use your data if you do not complete all the trials.\n When you are ready to start the experimental trials, please press space or touch the button below.&quot;;&amp;#10;" valType="extendedCode" updates="constant" name="Begin JS Routine"/>
        <Param val="instruction_text = &quot;You have completed the practice trials. During the experimental trials, you will not receive feedback, but it is very important that you respond as quickly and accurately as possible.\nBefore you begin, please ensure that you are in a comfortable and quiet location and will not be disturbed for about 10 minutes, as the experiment cannot be paused and we cannot use your data if you do not complete all the trials.\n When you are ready to start the experimental trials, please press space or touch the button below.&quot;" valType="extendedCode" updates="constant" name="Begin Routine"/>
